<https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/83000116/2025-26/evaluation> a ns1:EvaluationSystem ;
    ns1:evaluationDescription """The evaluation will comprise three items:
An initial quizz: 10%
A set of individual reports, including the calculations performed: 40%
An individual presentation where application of simulation software from the first part of the course will be applied to a realistic prototype: 25%
An individual presentation where application of simulation software from the second part of the course will be applied to a realistic prototype: 25%"""@es ;
